Clock PMS+ has two versions of the booking engine:- WRS v1 The booking engine was hostd on Clock PMS+ page and as such the scripts were directly installed in Clock PMS+ configurations;
. Send Script as normal, and ask BE to integrate inside the Iframe.
- WRS v2(also known as Book Direct) Where the booking engine overlaps the hotel's website and the tracking scripts are installed onto the hotel's website as described here and can exchange data with the booking engine. Send client this: Since WRS v2 is in use, there is a new way to add scripts and track conversions on the hotel's website. The scripts should be built and installed by your website administrator using the parameters from this article in order to pull data from WRS v2. For further guidance, there is also a live demo video from Clock explaining how to action this, see the link here.
